data.title: average
data.text: Drive through does not list doughnuts, Manufactured routine doughnuts.  Coffee good.If I didn't know better, I would have thought from the outdoor menu that I was at a drive through hamburger joint.

data.title: Coffee and Donuts
data.text: Coffee is freshly brewed and delicious. Just be careful when you take your first sip, it's hot! 😊 The Old Fashion donut was great.

data.title: Indifferent service
data.text:
There didn't seem to be many donuts on offer, so we asked the assistant if that was all he had. "Yeah" he said, then proceeded to stand right in front of the display cabinet so we couldn't see.

Anyway, we ordered a few donuts.  Unsmiling, he silently bagged up the donuts.  No please, thank you or anything.

It turns out it was 40 minutes before closing time, which is an excuse for not having many donuts left, but no excuse for poor service.
